OL,3,CIndependent review into maternity
OL,4,Cservices delayed
OL,6,FThe Independent Review of Maternity
OL,7,FServices, led by Donna Ockenden, have
OL,8,Fconfirmed that the publication date
OL,9,Ffor the Review's report will be
OL,10,Fdelayed.
OL,12,FThe report was scheduled to be
OL,13,Fpublished in September 2025, but has
OL,14,Fbeen delayed for a further year in
OL,15,Forder to incorporate more women and
OL,16,Ffamilies.
OL,18,FDonna Ockenden, who is chairing the
OL,19,Freview, said that the number of
OL,20,Ffamilies included would need to
OL,21,Fincrease by a further 300, to 2,500.
