OL,6,FThe reason for the increased number of
OL,7,Fcases stems from discrepancies between
OL,8,Fthe trust and the Review as to what
OL,9,Fcases should be considered.
OL,11,FSome cases of babies who have died,
OL,12,Fbabies with brain injury and mothers
OL,13,Fwho have died were not provided to the
OL,14,Freview.
OL,16,FDonna Ockenden did say that this has
OL,17,Farisen from "a genuine
OL,18,Fmisunderstanding".
