OL,3,CIndependent review into maternity
OL,4,Cservices delayed
OL,6,FAnthony May, Chief Executive of
OL,7,FNottingham University Hospitals NHS
OL,8,FTrust said: "It is important that we
OL,9,Fuse the Review to maximise learning
OL,10,Fand that all affected women and
OL,11,Ffamilies are included.
OL,13,F"I support fully the decision to
OL,14,Finclude new families, and I support
OL,15,Fthe decision to extend the timetable.
OL,17,F"Since the start of the Review in
OL,18,FSeptember 2022, we have worked closely
OL,19,Fwith Donna Ockenden and her team, and
OL,20,Fthis will continue through to the
OL,21,Freport's publication and beyond.
