OL,6,F"While the Review is ongoing, we will
OL,7,Fcontinue to do everything we can to
OL,8,Fimprove our maternity services further.
OL,10,F"It is clear that, thanks to a huge
OL,11,Famount of work from colleagues in the
OL,12,Fservice, we have achieved sustainable
OL,13,Fand evidenced improvements in our
OL,14,Fmaternity services.
OL,16,F"Women, families and the communities
OL,17,Fwe serve can be assured that our
OL,18,Fmaternity services are better now than
OL,19,Fthey were at the start of the Review."
